* BMAP phase-8 literals: "=expr" / "=Oexpr" numeric literals are interned --
* deduped by value -- into the LITERALS section (section 1), and each reference
* is relocated against that section.  =5 is shared by LDA and LDQ (one pool
* word); =O17 and =-1 add two more.  Pool: 5, 017, 777777777777.
       OUNAME LITTST
       LDA    =5
       ADA    =O17
       LDQ    =5
       STA    =-1
       END
